  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-13）：清华大学崔鹏团队推出 LimiX，打破任务壁垒，以 Transformer 架构引领结构化数据泛化",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500328&idx=1&sn=aa3285f3e833ee26adf6b784f354cefc",
  "date": "2025-11-13 10:11:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LimiX</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39351851851851855\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"458\" data-imgfileid=\"100016666\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c111b609&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWpylo9aTleFFX0yaL3qPStnQqBciclSsIXm1m8nVrruURTUdx1gthhxfu4J2ZQvLh1FrAekkSgvw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LimiX是LDM系列的首个项目，旨在推动通用性的发展。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过单一模型处理分类、回归、缺失值填补、特征选择、样本选择和因果推断等任务，促进从定制化管道到统一基础风格表格学习的转变。LimiX采用优化的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Transformer架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，专注于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">结构化数据建模</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">任务泛化</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。模型通过嵌入特征X和目标Y，将其转化为token表示，并在核心模块中应用注意力机制，以识别关键样本和特征中的显著模式。最终生成的高维表示被传递到回归和分类头，从而支持多样的预测任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/limix\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/limix</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：JustRL</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"466\" data-imgfileid=\"100016667\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79685524&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWpylo9aTleFFX0yaL3qPS3KHXOpmWH4ws6ibfWZb4mnB5eJzfumISmLfks5QVHsiaNNMkfUpZcJcQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★JustRL-DeepSeek-1.5B 是一个基于 DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-1.5B 的小型语言模型，专注于数学推理任务。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目展示了在不使用复杂多阶段管道或动态调度的情况下，如何通过单阶段训练和固定超参数实现竞争性的强化学习性能。JustRL-DeepSeek-1.5B 通过简单的训练配方和较少的计算资源，达到了与更复杂方法相媲美的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/justrl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/justrl</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：UNComp</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3824074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"444\" data-imgfileid=\"100016665\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0205e918&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWpylo9aTleFFX0yaL3qPSBK2DZCmDiaAdIrGquOibiaiaeXyLVJU0ib50SNCsNCKZ9ia5tdUzfoF1PgVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UNComp是一个不确定性感知的KV缓存压缩框架，专为长上下文大语言模型（LLMs）设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目利用截断矩阵熵揭示稀疏性，将缓存大小减少到原来的4.74%，并在几乎无性能损失的情况下提升吞吐量6倍。其两阶段框架能够联合压缩隐藏状态和KV缓存，加速预填充和解码过程。UNComp在多个基准测试中表现优异，甚至在9.38%的压缩比下也能匹敌完整的KV缓存。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uncomp\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uncomp</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：archgw</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3314814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"384\" data-imgfileid=\"100016664\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2fa6e4a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWpylo9aTleFFX0yaL3qPSTHbDicYtyaMF2YUn7V7vsh8Wbckx8NK2Nk331GKoQ0NU4xdUCb8HEgA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ArchGW是一个专为AI智能体设计的模型原生智能体服务器，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">旨在帮助开发者更快地构建和扩展智能体应用</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它处理AI开发中的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">繁琐工作</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，如智能体路由与交接、应用防护措施、无代码日志和追踪，以及统一访问OpenAI、Anthropic、Ollama等大型语言模型（LLM）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/archgw\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/archgw</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：DeepEyesV2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" data-height=\"450\" data-imgfileid=\"100016663\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=040daf26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWpylo9aTleFFX0yaL3qPSIA17Msicb4cTN8D4BdEmibx6t9PI0tzHQbptjuEhZAk2qYXmH0BiaCo2Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepEyesV2 是一个智能体多模态模型，能够在单一推理循环中统一代码执行和网页搜索，从而实现可靠且复杂的推理。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过严格的数据过滤和清洗，构建了冷启动 SFT 数据和 RL 数据，二者相辅相成。广泛的实验表明，DeepEyesV2 在真实世界理解、数学推理和搜索密集型基准测试中表现出强大的推理和工具使用能力。分析表明，DeepEyesV2 的工具使用行为具有任务自适应模式，强化学习可以实现更复杂的工具组合和自适应、上下文感知的工具调用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepeyesv2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepeyesv2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Rex-Omni</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"100016668\" data-ratio=\"0.26851851851851855\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=39cacab0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyWpylo9aTleFFX0yaL3qPShcEKEa8r4zGWvmjGy4KnMrD1YdXFpEot5AxyicycTAkYmSnot1xwkAw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Rex-Omni是一个拥有30亿参数的多模态大语言模型（MLLM），通过将目标检测和其他视觉感知任务重新定义为简单的下一个标记预测问题，提供了一种创新的解决方案。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目基于Qwen2.5-VL-3B模型，旨在通过高效的推理和量化技术，提升视觉任务的处理能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rex-omni\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/rex-omni</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章介绍了清华大学崔鹏团队的 LimiX 等多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖结构化数据泛化、小型语言模型、KV 缓存压缩、智能体服务器及多模态模型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章介绍了清华大学崔鹏团队的 LimiX 等多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖结构化数据泛化、小型语言模型、KV 缓存压缩、智能体服务器及多模态模型。",
  "summary": "本篇“今日开源”文章精选并介绍了多个近期在人工智能领域发布的开源项目。核心亮点包括清华大学崔鹏团队推出的 LimiX，它采用优化的 Transformer 架构，旨在打破结构化数据处理的任务壁垒，实现分类、回归、缺失值填补等多种任务的统一泛化。文章还提及了 JustRL，一个专注于数学推理的小型语言模型，以简洁的训练方法实现高效性能。在工具与框架方面，UNComp 作为针对长上下文大语言模型的不确定性感知的 KV 缓存压缩框架，显著提升了 LLM 的吞吐量和效率。ArchGW 则是一个模型原生智能体服务器，致力于简化 AI 智能体应用的开发与扩展。此外，文章还介绍了两个智能体多模态模型：DeepEyesV2 通过统一代码执行和网页搜索实现复杂推理，而 Rex-Omni 则是一个 30 亿参数的多模态大语言模型，创新性地将目标检测等视觉感知任务转化为标记预测问题。整体而言，文章为 AI 从业者提供了快速了解最新开源项目及其核心价值的窗口。",
